title: Mouse Guard - Winter 1152 (complete) (Minutemen)
description:
Mouse Guard - Winter 1152 #1-6 by David Petersen

Mouse Guard, the indie hit of 2006, returns with a second series! In the Winter of 1152, the Guard face a food and supply shortage threatening the lives of many through a cold and icy season. Serving as diplomats Saxon, Kenzie, Lieam, and Sadie, led by Celanawe, traverse the snow blanketed territories to improve relations between cities and the Guard. This is a winter not every Guard may survive.
